    {
      "id": "food",
      "label": { "en": "Food", "ja": "食事" },
      "body": {
        "en": "Daily food budgets are anchored to current Numbeo meal benchmarks for Osaka, Kyoto, and Tokyo, then adjusted into a practical day mix of one inexpensive meal, one stronger dinner/cafe moment, and snacks or drinks.",
        "ja": "食事はNumbeoの大阪・京都・東京の現行相場を基準にし、安めの食事1回、しっかりした食事やカフェ1回、軽食や飲み物を足した実用的な1日分へ調整しています。"
      },
      "links": [
        {
          "label": { "en": "Numbeo Osaka", "ja": "Numbeo 大阪" },
          "url": "https://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/in/Osaka/"
        },
        {
          "label": { "en": "Numbeo Kyoto", "ja": "Numbeo 京都" },
          "url": "https://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/in/Kyoto/"
        },
        {
          "label": { "en": "Numbeo Tokyo", "ja": "Numbeo 東京" },
          "url": "https://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/in/Tokyo/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "attractions",
      "label": { "en": "Attractions", "ja": "観光・チケット" },
      "body": {
        "en": "Ticketed attractions use current public prices that match this route: Mt. Fuji Panorama Ropeway, SHIBUYA SKY, and TOKYO SKYTREE. Days without a strong ticket anchor stay conservative and let contingency or optional extras absorb smaller admissions.",
        "ja": "チケット系は、この旅程に直接合う富士山パノラマロープウェイ、SHIBUYA SKY、TOKYO SKYTREEの現行公開料金を使っています。はっきりしたチケット基準がない日は、控えめに見積もり、細かな入場料は予備費や任意費用で吸収します。"
      },
      "links": [
        {
          "label": { "en": "Mt. Fuji Panorama Ropeway", "ja": "富士山パノラマロープウェイ" },
          "url": "https://www.mtfujiropeway.jp/en/price-hours/"
        },
        {
          "label": { "en": "GO TOKYO SHIBUYA SKY", "ja": "GO TOKYO SHIBUYA SKY" },
          "url": "https://www.gotokyo.org/en/spot/1732/index.html"
        },
        {
          "label": { "en": "TOKYO SKYTREE ticket prices", "ja": "TOKYO SKYTREE料金" },
          "url": "https://www.tokyo-skytree.jp/en/ticket/individual/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "shoppingBuffer",
      "label": { "en": "Shopping / discretionary buffer", "ja": "買い物・裁量バッファ" },
      "body": {
        "en": "This is an explicit planning cushion layered on top of sourced food and ticket costs. It stays light on Osaka/Kyoto days and grows on Fuji/Tokyo days where weather pivots, souvenirs, or extra cafes are more likely.",
        "ja": "これは、出典のある食事・チケット費に上乗せする明示的な計画バッファです。大阪・京都では軽め、天候変更や土産、カフェが増えやすい富士・東京では厚めにしています。"
      },
      "links": [
        {
          "label": { "en": "Food sources", "ja": "食事の出典" },
          "url": "https://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/in/Tokyo/"
        },
        {
          "label": { "en": "Attraction sources", "ja": "観光の出典" },
          "url": "https://www.tokyo-skytree.jp/en/ticket/individual/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "contingency",
      "label": { "en": "Contingency / misc", "ja": "予備費・雑費" },
      "body": {
        "en": "Contingency is a transparent misc cushion for lockers, platform snacks, weather changes, coin laundry, and small routing misses. It deliberately scales up on the heavier transfer days instead of pretending the trip runs perfectly.",
        "ja": "予備費は、ロッカー、ホームでの軽食、天候変更、コインランドリー、小さな乗り継ぎミスを吸収するための明示的な雑費です。すべて完璧に進む前提にはせず、移動の重い日に厚めにしています。"
      },
      "links": [
        {
          "label": { "en": "Transit basis", "ja": "移動の基準" },
          "url": "https://smart-ex.jp/en/product/plan/service/pdf/service_fares_reserved.pdf"
        },
        {
          "label": { "en": "Food basis", "ja": "食事の基準" },
          "url": "https://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/in/Tokyo/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "optionalExtras",
      "label": { "en": "Optional extras", "ja": "任意の追加費用" },
      "body": {
        "en": "Optional extras are the non-essential flex layer: dessert stops, nicer drinks, one more paid view, or a small splurge dinner. The toggle keeps them separate from the core estimate so the total stays understandable.",
        "ja": "任意の追加費用は、デザート、少し良い飲み物、もう1つの有料展望、少し贅沢な夕食などの柔軟な出費です。トグルで基礎見積もりから分け、合計を分かりやすく保ちます。"
      },
